      },
      "date": "2018-05-15 21:52:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1\n\nLet's wait for feedback on the upstream patch, and when that is settled down this one can be updated to match.  That avoids the need to change the /sys interface if it is different in the upstream kernel.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
